defmodule Solution do
  @spec beautiful_indices(s :: String.t, a :: String.t, b :: String.t, k :: integer) :: [integer]
  def beautiful_indices(s, a, b, k) do
    a_indices = for i <- 0..(String.length(s) - String.length(a)), 
                    String.slice(s, i, String.length(a)) == a, do: i

    b_indices = for j <- 0..(String.length(s) - String.length(b)), 
                    String.slice(s, j, String.length(b)) == b, do: j

    Enum.filter(a_indices, fn i -> 
      Enum.any?(b_indices, fn j -> abs(i - j) <= k end)
    end)
  end
end
